<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>: <span class="c2">(الزَّلْهُ)</span> :) أَهْمَلَهُ الجوْهرِيُّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ الأعْرابيِّ:</span> هُوَ <span class="c2">(نَوْرُ الرَّيحانِ وحُسْنُه)</span> .<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(قالَ: (و)</span> أَيْضاً: <span class="c2">(الصَّخْرَةُ)</span> الَّتِي <span class="c2">(يقومُ عَلَيْهَا السَّاقِي)</span> .<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(قالَ: (و)</span> أَيْضاً: <span class="c2">(التَّحَيُّرُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>(و) قالَ اللّيْثُ: الزَّلَهُ، <span class="c2">(مُحرَّكاً: مَا يَصِلُ إِلَى النَّفسِ من غَمِّ)</span> الحاجَةِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>